Paper: hep-th/9403169

Date: 1994-03-28

Title: Classical Electrodynamics with Dual Potentials

Authors: M. Baker, James S. Ball, F. Zachariasen

Comments: 18 pages, 3 figures not included, CALT-68-1890

We present Dirac's method for using dual potentials to solve classicalelectrodynamics for an oppositely charged pair of particles, with a view toextending these techniques to non-Abelian gauge theories.